data.description: This property sits on a dead-end street with one way in and one out.  Waterpark for the kids is just two blocks away.  Open den and dining room with nice brick fireplace.  New energy-saving vinyl windows throughout were installed in 2021.  The kitchen boasts a pantry and a wall of cabinets for all the kitchen gadgets.  French doors open onto a nice patio for entertaining—a large backyard for the kids and dog with a six-foot privacy fence.  Bedrooms are spacious with large windows for natural lighting.  New roof was installed in November 2023.
